Everything works great. I am only having one issue with Beatcraft. After I make my beats and render the sequence to an audio file, the audio files will not play. They wont open up with any program. Also when I look at the rendered audio files they have a little lock symbol on them. Anyone got a fix for this?

Ok guys n Gals good news. I have just found out that you have to run beatcraft as administrator. This has now allowed me to play back my rendered beats in programs such as windows media player and other recording software.
Thanks,buddy.
